# AIRCMS Project Demonstration Video

This video demonstrates the working of the **AI-Powered Job Recruitment & Candidate Management System (AIRCMS)** developed on Salesforce.

The demonstration covers:

- Lightning Recruitment Application
- Job Opening Management
- Candidate Application Creation
- Screen Flow Automation
- Approval Process Workflow
- AI Candidate Scoring
- Recruitment Workspace Navigation

